The high conductivity of BLSO provided profound electromagnetic shielding capability. We measured shielding effectiveness (SE) using the coaxial transmission line method. Figure 5 shows the SE of BLSO(0001)Al2O3BaZrO3/MgO\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
