				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{BLSO}}_{(0001){\mathrm{Al}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{3}}^{{\mathrm{BaZrO}}_{3}/\mathrm{MgO}}$$\end{document} is promising as a TC material for stealth technology, as also evidenced by its larger absorptivity (> 0.7 at 10 GHz) than reflectivity (< 0.2) (Additional file 1: Fig. S12). Our BLSO films will attract attention by virtue of having a low sheet resistance, high transmittance, high shielding effectiveness, chemical and mechanical stability, and easy coating fabrication process covering a wide range of applications.Fig. 5
